{"tid":181781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（肥毒福音）非洲部落美男選舉，大肚腩先最有型","createTime":"2017-03-31T23:43:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T00:23:47.000Z","uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d0a993f41c38c763d6a4def49d4080aa00c6c1f","tid":181781,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T23:43:41.000Z","msg":"埃塞俄比亞博迪部落（Bodi）的男士要擁有龐大腰圍才叫吸引，各家庭要選出一名未婚男子，花半年時間飲新鮮牛奶及牛血增肥，務求養出巨型肚腩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n來到決勝負當日，參實者用泥及灰塗抹身體&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;勝出者並無實質獎品，但可贏到面子以及女士們的愛慕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/nintchdbpict000312298551.jpg?strip=all&amp;w=960&amp;quality=100\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2Fnintchdbpict000312298551.jpg%3Fstrip%3Dall%26w%3D960%26quality%3D100&h=9fa21bb3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"075e26adc31af0c549e2139f8cb327a7e53d64f5","tid":181781,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T23:56:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a5b823b8138e1ac55ca6ed8001d221e1661d8b","tid":181781,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T00:00:48.000Z","msg":"圖中個男人個肚幾多個月大？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61cf707eb89973d4db628532dd85d216653602c","tid":181781,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T00:23:47.000Z","msg":"係果到有大肚腩姐係代表有錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}